{"tid":1796504,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人地德國佬想拍片支持我地！","createTime":"2019-12-24T16:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T14:35:40.000Z","uid":189233,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8e3290f8d470f815497fac12cd1f40ce2db86819","tid":1796504,"uid":189233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:09:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">人地德國佬起kickstarter搞緊個眾籌，講年輕既抗爭者點推動社會，佢簡左三個地方</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>包括烏干達、<span style=\"color: maroon;\">香港</span>、美國</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gakoY9R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgakoY9R.png&h=582a1fbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/youngactivists/prayers-do-nothing-a-film-about-young-activists-worldwide/description\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2Fyoungactivists%2Fprayers-do-nothing-a-film-about-young-activists-worldwide%2Fdescription&d=nB3K3ojK8rN8kNU4dsXAY9%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=517f9290\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/youngactivists/prayers-do-nothing-a-film-about-young-activists-worldwide/description</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">既然大家咁想要有<strong>國際戰線</strong>，有影片流傳係一件好好既證明，特別係人地國家自己拍、自己剪片既時候，而佢主題要融入年輕者抗爭，更加將我地既概念<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>打上一層樓</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><blockquote>we are a generation of scared people, but very ambitious, very united, very persistence and very good at action.<br />\n<br />\n- hilda flavia nakabuye</blockquote></span><br />\n<br />\n都係kickstarter既project，大家仲唔快d去留言同課金支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"h